        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/3/132/2",
        "text": [
          " : «كَانَ أَبِي عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَنْزِلُ اَلْحَصْبَةَ قَلِيلاً ثُمَّ يَرْتَحِلُ وَ هُوَ دُونَ خَبْطٍ وَ حِرْمَانٍ »."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.3028 – Imam (as) said: \"My father (as) would stop briefly at al-Hasba and then depart, and it is a place below Khabt and Hirman.\""
          ]
        }
